## MySQL Exporter Environment

DATA_SOURCE_NAME="monitor:password@(mysql:3306)/"

## PostgreSQL Exporter Environment

DATA_SOURCE_NAME="postgresql://monitor:password@postgres:5432/postgres?sslmode=disable"

## Start Monitoring Platform

docker-compose up -d

## Verify Exporters

MySQL Exporter

http://localhost:9104/metrics

PostgreSQL Exporter

http://localhost:9187/metrics
